body_html:
@mtanana I tried your solution. It seems to be working, but there is some warmings, such as
**
tensorflow/stream_executor/cuda/cuda_fft.cc:327] Unable to load cuFFT DSO.
I tensorflow/stream_executor/dso_loader.cc:77] LD_LIBRARY_PATH: /usr/local/cuda-7.5/lib64:/usr/local/cuda-7.5/lib64:/usr/local/cuda-7.5/lib64:
I tensorflow/stream_executor/cuda/cuda_rng.cc:317] Unable to load cuRAND DSO.
**

does these warming matters or we can ignore it?
